-- Vodafone May Get $4.5 Billion From Verizon, Sunday Times Says
-- B y   E m m a   C h a r l t o n
-- 2012-07-15T10:17:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-15/vodafone-may-get-4-5-billion-from-verizon-sunday-times-says.html
Vodafone Group Plc (VOD)  may get a
dividend of $4.5 billion from Verizon Wireless, its U.S. venture
with  Verizon Communications Inc. (VZ) , the  Sunday Times  reported,
without saying where it got the information.  The Newbury, England-based company will probably pass the
money on to shareholders in the form of a special dividend, the
newspaper report said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emma Charlton in London at 
